……”\\n\\n周围的魔教成员们神情各异，有的贪婪，有的嗜血，有的警惕，有的则面无表情，但无一不透着一股令人不寒而栗的邪气。你混迹其中，小心地观察着一切，等待着接下来的指令或变故。\\n\\n<details class=\\\"st-details st-gothic-vampire\\\" open style=\\\"margin-top:15px; margin-bottom:10px; border:2px solid #4B0000; border-radius:4px; background-color:#1A0000; color:#E0C2C2; font-family: 'Cinzel Decorative', 'UnifrakturMaguntia', 'Metamorphous', serif; font-size:16px; box-shadow: 0 0 20px rgba(139,0,0,0.6), inset 0 0 15px rgba(128,0,0,0.4); text-shadow: 1px 1px 3px rgba(0,0,0,0.7);\\\">\\n<summary class=\\\"st-summary\\\" style=\\\"padding:10px 15px; cursor:pointer; font-weight:bold; color:#FFD1D1; background:linear-gradient(to right, #3B0000, #5C0000, #3B0000); border-bottom:2px groove #6A0000; border-radius:3px 3px 0 0; display:flex; justify-content:space-between; align-items:center; letter-spacing:1px;\\\">\\n  <span><i class=\\\"fas fa-skull-crossbones\\\" style=\\\"margin-right:10px; color:#FF7F7F; filter: drop-shadow(0 0 3px #FF0000);\\\"></i>† {{user}} 当前密令 †</span>\\n  <span class=\\\"st-toggle-icon\\\" style=\\\"font-size:0.8em; color:#D2B48C; font-family: 'Times New Roman', serif;\\\">[开/闭]</span>\\n</summary>\\n<div class=\\\"st-content\\\" style=\\\"padding:15px 20px; line-height:1.75; border-top:1px solid #400000; background:rgba(0,0,0,0.2);\\\">\\n  <p style=\\\"margin:8px 0; border-bottom:1px solid #500000; padding-bottom:6px;\\\"><strong style=\\\"color:#FFA07A; min-width:90px; display:inline-block;\\\">🍷 代号/真名:</strong> <span id=\\\"user_nickname_value_mojiao\\\" style=\\\"color:#FFC0CB; font-weight:bold; text-shadow: 0 0 5px #FF0000;\\\">{{user}} (由你设定)</span></p>\\n  <p style=\\\"margin:8px 0; border-bottom:1px solid #500000; padding-bottom:6px;\\\"><strong style=\\\"color:#FFA07A; min-width:90px; display:inline-block;\\\">⚰️ 所属/派系:</strong> <span id=\\\"user_identity_value_mojiao\\\" style=\\\"color:#E9967A;\\\">[鬼王宗/万毒门/合欢派/长生堂等，由你设定]</span></p>\\n  <p style=\\\"margin:8px 0; border-bottom:1px solid #500000; padding-bottom:6px;\\\"><s